    • Method Detail

      • getRenderedFacetsAndChildren

        protected Iterator<javax.faces.component.UIComponent> getRenderedFacetsAndChildren(javax.faces.context.FacesContext facesContext)
        UIXShowDetail only allows processing of its children when it is disclosed. However ShowDetailHeader has other facets like toolbar etc that need to be processed even then it is not disclosed. So override the functionality from UIXShowDetail and pass it along to the default functionality where-in the renderer decides which children need to be processed
        Overrides:
        getRenderedFacetsAndChildren in class org.apache.myfaces.trinidad.component.UIXShowDetail
        Parameters:
        facesContext - the faces context
        Returns:
        an iterator of UI Components.
